"The following is a true story (I think!). In 1973, the University of "
"California, Berkeley had some worries about the admissions of students into "
"their postgraduate courses. Specifically, the thing that caused the problem "
"was that the gender breakdown of their admissions, which looked like this:"
msgstr ""
"Følgende er en sann historie (tror jeg!). I 1973 hadde University of "
"California, Berkeley, noen problemer med opptaket av studenter til sine "
"doktorgradskurs. Problemet var at kjønnsfordelingen ved opptaket så slik ut:"

#: ../../Ch01/Ch01_WhyStats_3.rst:15
msgid "Number of applicants"
msgstr "Antall søkere"

